  "body": "Split off from #4713.\r\n\r\nOnce the dashboard can easily switch between mainnet, public testnets, and truffle's managed networks, there still remains the issue of funding those accounts in the that are brought from the wallet in the managed networks.\r\n\r\nWhen the user switches to one of these managed networks, we should probably detect whether the currently imported accounts are funded. If not, we should notify them while also prompting them for the amount to fund each account with.\r\n\r\nWhile they are connected to one of these managed networks, they should be able to re-fund their account at any time.",
